---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-surface-950 text-gray-300 py-12 mt-auto">
  <div class="container-site">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
      <div>
        <p class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-white mb-2">
          <span class="text-brand-500">Coach</span>Techno
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          J'aide les PME et professionnels à utiliser l'IA pour sauver du temps et automatiser leur travail.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-white mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Navigation</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="/coaching-technologique" class="hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Coaching technologique</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog" class="hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href="/a-propos" class="hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">À propos</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-white mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Contact</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">
              Réserver une consultation
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">
              LinkedIn
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-surface-700 pt-6 text-center text-xs text-gray-500">
      &copy; {year} Jimmy Gilbert — CoachTechno. Tous droits réservés.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
